  <brief_title>A Study of OPC-262 in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, 3-arms Parallel Group Comparative Study of OPC-262 in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes (Phase 2/3 Study)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
