  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this clinical study is to evaluate the superiority of the efficacy of OPC-262
      (2.5 mg, and 5 mg) to placebo in patients with type 2 diabetes after 24 week treatment in a
      double-blind fashion and to evaluate the safety of OPC-262 to placebo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
